            "title": "Our story",
            "text": "<p>Welcome to the world of <strong>TIME</strong>, the flagship brand of Bioweal Products. Our journey started with a simple yet powerful idea to provide products that care as much about women’s health as they do about the planet.</p><p> As a proudly Indian brand, we’re committed to making a difference in how menstrual care is perceived and experienced. From being one of the top organic sanitary pads brands in India to pioneering sustainable choices, our goal is to empower women to live their lives uninterrupted.</p><p>At TIME Pads, every product we create reflects our core values of care, quality, and sustainability—because every woman deserves the best, every time.</p>",
