          "settings": {
            "enable_image": false,
            "shape_class": "",
            "title": "",
            "text": "<h3><strong>Thoughtful Design</strong></h3><p><strong><br/></strong>Our sanitary pads are crafted with precision and care to provide functionality that complements your lifestyle and Leak-Proof Protection. We understand the importance of details, and that's why every product is designed with you in mind. Whether it is leak guards, higher absorbency, ultra thin design, ultra wide back, extra long pads, we have carefully detailed in our product design.</p>",
            "button_label": "",
            "button_link": "",
