            "heading_text": "We Care About the Small Things",
            "paragraph_text": "<p>At <strong>TIME Pads</strong>, the smallest details matter because we create the biggest impact. From skin-safe materials to eco-friendly choices, every element is designed with care—for your comfort, your health, and the planet. It’s the little things that define true care, and we never overlook them.</p>",
